<L><PB N="121" REF="124">
Proud of thy fleets and armies, &s;tol'n the gem</L>
<L>Of his ju&s;t prai&s;e to lavi&s;h it on them?</L>
<L>Ha&s;t thou not learn'd what thou art often told,</L>
