<L>And rais'd thy&s;elf, a greater, in their &s;tead,</L>
<L><PB N="122" REF="125">
Gone thither arm'd and hungry, returned full,</L>
<L>Fed from the riche&s;t veins of the Mogul,</L>
<L>A de&s;pot big with pow'r obtain'd by wealth,</L>
